{"div":{"@":{"xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","type":"article","xml:id":"MG-1694-09_007","resp":"wordpro"},"#":[{"head":{"value":"[Conseils donnez à l’Espagne]","id":"/div/#[0]/head"}},{"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/#[1]/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", septembre 1694 [tome 9], p. 7-13.","id":"/div/#[1]/bibl/#"}}},{"p":{"value":"Il n’y a point de Pays si éloigné qui ne retentisse des justes loüanges que l’on donne au Roy. C’est en toutes sortes de Langues que l’on parle de cette admirable superiorité de Genie, de Prudence &amp; de Sagesse, qui le rend le plus grand de tous les hommes, &amp; vous ne serez pas fâchée qu’aprés vous avoir fait voir le Portrait de cet Auguste Monarque en plusieurs Sonnets Italiens que contiennent quelques-unes de mes Lettres, je vous fasse entendre aujourd’huy ce qu’une Muse Espagnole conseille à ceux de cette superbe Nation, par les Quatrains que vous allez lire.","id":"/div/#[2]/p"}},{"quote":{"#":[{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Españoles, el remedio","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[0]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’el Vencedor os ofreçe","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[0]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Para España que pereçe,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[0]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Es no desechar su medio.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[0]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[1]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" El Christianissimo Rey","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[2]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Con la paz os da buen logro,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[2]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Y nunca os pondreis en cobro","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[2]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si no admitis esta ley.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[2]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[3]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Mientras en la guerra dais,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[4]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"El Rey pierde quanto tiene,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[4]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Y pues la paz le convienne,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[4]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Porque la menospreciais ?","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[4]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[5]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" De vos se burlan en Françia,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[6]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Viendo os tan sin mesura,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[6]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sin animo, ni cordura,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[6]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Blasonar tanta arrogançia.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[6]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[7]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Juzgad que no os estan bien","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[8]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Humos de tiempos passados ;","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[8]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Oy los echos acertados,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[8]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Es mirar quando y con quien.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[8]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[9]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Y a Carlos Quinto en el mundo","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[10]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"No da fuerza à l’altivez ;","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[10]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Su medalla esta al reves,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[10]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Reynando Carlos Segundo.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[10]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[11]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Y si Carlos Quinto fuera","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[12]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Oy el Monarca d’España,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[12]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"El gran Luis en Campaña","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[12]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"No menos triumphos tuviera.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[12]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[13]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Antes serian mayores","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[14]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Como se echa de ver,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[14]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quan mayores son vencer","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[14]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Reyes que son Vençedores.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[14]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[15]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" El Frances, sin que lo piense,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[16]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ve como la suerte os huye.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[16]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si os acomete, os destruye,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[16]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Y si lo envestis, os vençe","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[16]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[17]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Ved vuestra sangre vertida,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[18]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vuestra tierra saqueada,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[18]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Destruyda vuestra armada,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[18]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Y vuestra fama perdida.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[18]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[19]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Pues aquel que en tal abismo","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[20]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pensais que os puede valer,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[20]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Harto tiene que hazer","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[20]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Para valer se a si mismo.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[20]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[21]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Y assi mientras ay lugar,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[22]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tratad de paz, pues es çierto","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[22]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’el medio que veis abierto","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[22]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Se puede presto cerrar.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/#[22]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}}]}},{"p":{"value":"C’est avec raison que l’Auteur de ces Quatrains a fait connoistre aux Espagnols, en leur conseillant de faire la Paix, que la fierté qu’ils se permettoient autrefois, ne sçauroit leur convenir aujourd’huy, &amp; qu’il est de la prudence de se conduire selon les temps, &amp; de regarder quand &amp; avec qui, puisque si Charles V. regnoit encore en Espagne au lieu de Charles II. Louis le Grand ne remporteroit pas moins de triomphes. Au contraire ils brilleroient avec plus d’éclat, puisqu’il y a plus de gloire à vaincre des Rois, qui se sont rendus fameux par d’importantes Conquestes.","id":"/div/#[4]/p"}}]}}